-It is too dangerous.

606
01:07:50,524 --> 01:07:55,028
If we are captured,
Governor Odious shall surely kill her.

607
01:07:56,989 --> 01:07:58,990
You mentioned Odious?

608
01:08:00,493 --> 01:08:02,243
He is my sworn enemy.

609
01:08:03,079 --> 01:08:04,579
And my fiancé.

610
01:08:32,942 --> 01:08:33,983
No.

611
01:08:37,196 --> 01:08:39,697
I want to look at you until I die.

612
01:08:43,160 --> 01:08:46,037
What a mystery this world.

613
01:08:46,122 --> 01:08:48,581
One day you love them

614
